<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When converting an html document to text, the class Zend_Search_Lucene_Document_Html add spaces after each dom node, and so after each html closing tag.</p>

<p>For example, html "<b>Zend</b>Framework" (without space) will be returned as "Zend Framework".
Then the search query "ZendFramework" (no space) won't find this document.</p>

    </div>
</div>

